---
model: "gemini-3.1-flash-lite-preview"
config:
  temperature: 0.3
input:
  schema:
    topic:
      type: "string"
      description: "The subject or phrasal verb to visualize (e.g., 'Kitchen Utensils', 'Come across', 'Newton's Laws')"
    numConcepts:
      type: "integer"
      description: "The number of items to generate"
      default: 10
output:
  format: "json"
  schema:
    type: "object"
    required: [title, layout_style, items]
    properties:
      title:
        type: "string"
        description: "A clean, accurate title for the topic"
      layout_style:
        type: "string"
        enum: ["Flat-Lay", "Comic-Grid", "Diagram-Grid"]
        description: "Flat-Lay (objects), Comic-Grid (actions/verbs), or Diagram-Grid (abstract/science)"
      items:
        type: "array"
        items:
          type: "object"
          required: [number, term, definition]
          properties:
            number:
              type: "integer"
              minimum: 1
              maximum: 20
            term:
              type: "string"
              description: "The name of the item, action, or concept"
            definition:
              type: "string"
              description: "A short explanation for the app UI, explaining what this concept means."
---
{{role "system"}}
You are an Educational Data API. Your job is to take a user's topic and break it down into exactly {{numConcepts}} essential educational components.

Rules:
- Determine the best visual layout for the topic from these three options: Flat-Lay (for objects), Comic-Grid (for actions/verbs), or Diagram-Grid (for abstract/science concepts).
- The term should be the core concept name.
- The definition should be a concise summary of what this term means. This definition provides context to an AI image generator that will later draw it.

JSON Schema to Output:
{
  "title": "String (A clean title)",
  "layout_style": "String (Flat-Lay, Comic-Grid, or Diagram-Grid)",
  "items": [
    {
      "number": "Integer (1-20)",
      "term": "String (The name of the item/concept)",
      "definition": "String (A short conversational explanation of the concept)"
    }
  ]
}

{{role "user"}}
Generate the educational breakdown for the topic: {{topic}}
